title: Türisalu Cliff
text:
Türisalu Cliff is a cliff in <a href="T%C3%BCrisalu">Türisalu</a>, <a href="Estonia">Estonia</a>. The cliff is part of the <a href="Baltic%20Klint">Baltic Klint</a> and has a height of up to .
Türisalu cliff has accumulated a negative reputation as a "popular" place for <a href="suicide">suicide</a>s, especially among younger people.
